4240,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-30 17:48:29+00:00,96832580,Instagram/MonkeyType,61586,carljm,549085,Instagram,282676977,361675908,"@msoedov Thanks for the suggestion! Can you clarify what semantics you'd envision for `monkeytype apply .`? Would it try to apply all stubs present in the trace store? Or all stubs for modules within the current working directory (recursively)? The dot suggests the latter to me.

