4302,IssueCommentEvent,2016-01-05 18:55:05+00:00,39404445,mapbox/mapbox-sdk-py,1151287,perrygeo,600935,mapbox,100349404,169096660,"Python 2 support? I think Python 2 will be around for a long long time to come, most likely even after official support ends in 2020. We should support it until at least then.

