5445,IssueCommentEvent,2016-02-11 21:34:04+00:00,15720872,wq/django-rest-pandas,1530030,jrowen,1863683,wq,110469432,183067224,"I am running into this same permission error on Windows machines but found the update below seemed to eliminate the error.
```
from tempfile import NamedTemporaryFile

class PandasFileRenderer(PandasBaseRenderer):
    """"""
    Renderer for output formats that absolutely must use a file (i.e. Excel)
    """"""
    def init_output(self):
        fp = NamedTemporaryFile(suffix='.' + self.format, delete=False)
        self.filename = fp.name
        fp.close()

    def get_pandas_args(self, data):
        return [self.filename]

    def get_output(self):
        file = open(self.filename, 'rb')
        result = file.read()
        file.close()
        os.unlink(self.filename)
        return result
```",{},,User,False
