5639,IssueCommentEvent,2017-04-08 00:22:28+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,35314,cva,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,220334560,292680765,"In case anyone runs across this later and also trying to use iam signBlob, here's a snippet of what ended up working:

```python
    import google.auth
    credentials, project_id = google.auth.default(
        scopes=['https://www.googleapis.com/auth/iam'])

    import google.auth.transport.requests
    request = google.auth.transport.requests.Request()
    credentials.refresh(request)

    import google.auth.iam
    signer = google.auth.iam.Signer(
        request,
        credentials,
        credentials.service_account_email)

    signature = signer.sign(to_sign)
```",{},,User,False
