6616,IssueCommentEvent,2017-05-16 01:25:10+00:00,17712127,CoreSecurity/pcapy,3599441,guyharris,6544688,CoreSecurity,206425966,301648939,"> Which is strange because pcapy should be able to use the en0 interface when it's already been put into monitor mode through some other means

