7402,IssueCommentEvent,2015-12-15 20:12:08+00:00,26516210,letsencrypt/letsencrypt,1863453,pierreozoux,9289019,letsencrypt,120741597,164882962,"I don't like Linus language, but this is another debate.

Docker is not the recommend way, and it is targeted at power users.
 https://github.com/pierreozoux/letsencrypt/blob/master/docs/using.rst#running-with-docker

And power user should configure well their docker.
https://docs.docker.com/engine/installation/ubuntulinux/#create-a-docker-group

