7507,IssueCommentEvent,2015-01-25 17:06:03+00:00,4235447,django-salesforce/django-salesforce,181098,philchristensen,9872531,django-salesforce,55349243,71381346,"So you found a bug in the Salesforce v32.0 API because of the django-salesforce unit tests? That's great!

