7647,IssueCommentEvent,2017-07-28 21:57:12+00:00,14284859,marshmallow-code/marshmallow,12795061,AlecsGherghel,10334301,marshmallow-code,242527141,318771203,"Do we have a resolution for this? Seems like this is a recurring issue (https://github.com/marshmallow-code/marshmallow-sqlalchemy/issues/67)

As a side note: I injected the session in fields.py, around here:
`self.__schema = self.nested(many=self.many,
                        only=only, exclude=self.exclude, context=context,
                        load_only=self._nested_normalized_option('load_only'),
                        dump_only=self._nested_normalized_option('dump_only'),
                        session=db.session)`
and this indeed solves the problem with deserialization.

However, getting the session passed there seems to be pretty interesting.",{},,User,False
