8441,IssueCommentEvent,2018-03-21 17:10:00+00:00,91379993,tensorflow/tensorboard,710113,nfelt,15658638,tensorflow,307317349,375021668,"This sounds like the same issue that was reported in #682.  Are you using a machine with unicode (non-ASCII) characters in its hostname?

