9121,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-18 10:05:43+00:00,68402336,streamlink/streamlink,10303377,max-verem,22243823,streamlink,286924097,358598479,"my fix is:
```
diff --git a/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py b/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
index 4feee23..cca05fc 100644
--- a/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
+++ b/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
@@ -209,7 +209,7 @@ class YouTube(Plugin):

         params = {
             ""video_id"": video_id,
-            ""el"": ""player_embedded""
+            ""el"": ""embedded""
         }
         res = http.get(API_VIDEO_INFO, params=params, headers=HLS_HEADERS)
         return parse_query(res.text, name=""config"", schema=_config_schema)
```

if it still not work (you get **No playable streams found on this URL**)  like this:
```
[root@dev-5 streamlink.git]# streamlink ""https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI"" best
[cli][info] streamlink is running as root! Be careful!
[cli][info] Found matching plugin youtube for URL https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI
error: No playable streams found on this URL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI
```

next patch:
```
diff --git a/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py b/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
index cca05fc..f63cf02 100644
--- a/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
+++ b/src/streamlink/plugins/youtube.py
@@ -208,10 +208,13 @@ class YouTube(Plugin):
             return

         params = {
+            ""gl"": ""US"",
+            ""hl"": ""en"",
             ""video_id"": video_id,
             ""el"": ""embedded""
         }
         res = http.get(API_VIDEO_INFO, params=params, headers=HLS_HEADERS)
+        self.logger.debug(""res.text={0}"", res.text);
         return parse_query(res.text, name=""config"", schema=_config_schema)

     def _get_streams(self):
```

 could make a answer clear:
```
[root@dev-5 streamlink.git]# streamlink --loglevel debug ""https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI"" best
[cli][info] streamlink is running as root! Be careful!
[cli][info] Found matching plugin youtube for URL https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI
[plugin.youtube][debug] res.text=reason=%3Ca+href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_STrHbv2ZKI%26feature%3Dplayer_embedded%22+target%3D%22_blank%22%3EWatch+this+video+on+YouTube.%3C%2Fa%3E%0APlayback+on+other+websites+has+been+disabled+by+the+video+owner.&status=fail&errordetail=0&errorcode=150
error: No playable streams found on this URL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_STrHbv2ZKI
```

reason is **Playback+on+other+websites+has+been+disabled+by+the+video+owner.**

",{},NONE,User,False
